comments: Durant (BKN) and Temple (NOP) briefly engage and disengage. Temple's ability to defend is not affected.
Harris (BKN) ends his dribble and hops consecutively on the same foot after his gather.
Griffin (BKN) legally contests Valanciunas' (NOP) shot attempt.
Griffin (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Alexander-Walker (NOP) and firms up to absorb the contact during the pick.
Hart (NOP) turns into Griffin (BKN) and makes contact to his body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) makes marginal contact with Hart (NOP) during the entry pass that does not affect his ability to receive the pass.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) legally contests Harden's (BKN) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) slides his pivot foot upon receiving the ball.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) makes contact to Harden's (BKN) arm after the inbound.
The Nets are the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Pelicans.
Griffin (BKN) legally blocks Valanciunas' (NOP) shot near the rim.
Hart (NOP) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
